=Logic adding regions to a folder=
A folder track is a track that groups other tracks into a folder in the arrange window. To use it , follow these steps.



'''1.''' Select the regions you wish to add to the folder track.

'''2.''' Select '''Region''' / '''Folder''' / '''Pack folder'''



[[Image:Logic pack folder.png]]




This will place the selected regions into a folder track.

You can double click the folder track to view its contents.

If you wish to unpack the folder you can select the folder then go to '''Region''' / '''Folder''' / 
and choose either '''Unpack Folder (Create New Tracks)''' or '''Unpack Folder (Use existing Tracks)'''



[[Image:Logic Folder track menu.png]]


